This is a my work of building Online weather app.

To make run this application in your machine you need to use python version above 9.3.

I also provided my virtualenvironment on the environment have all required libraries("myenv\Scripts\activate").

If you need to create your own environment make use of required.txt file to install required libraries.

The database is also provide by myself you no need to worried about the database.

#####
Important Note:
"""Please Make sure you have a internet connection with out internet it gives connection Error"""

the Views of the application.

1) Login Interface

    *) To Login in to the app.
    *) Use this username and Password ot login.
    *) UserName = admin
    *) Password = admin123 

2) Update Interftace

    *) To update the value of the cities.
    *) And Display the weather Data of the all cities.

3) Search Interface

    *) To Get the weather information of the specific city.

4) Add and Delete Interface

    *) To add the new city to the database.
    *) To delete the existing city from the database.

5) Logout Interface

    *) To Logout the Authenticated username.
    *) And rediracted to Login Interface.

